{"tid":319324,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好冇人有時會同現任啲前度比較","createTime":"2017-07-12T16:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T06:41:58.000Z","uid":96402,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"135a11df97fdf1cbd34d515a6e4209fcb2ff5d0d","tid":319324,"uid":96402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:46:31.000Z","msg":"尋日無意中問下佢自己同佢啲前度某方面邊個好啲 <br />\n其實唔係真係話好care 算係話題一種<br />\n佢上一任係一個一齊咗兩年嘅女仔<br />\n佢突然話上一個係最好嘅 <br />\n冇嘢比得上佢上一任<br />\n嗰下sad到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢完全唔察覺呢句嘢嘅殺傷力<br />\n我知每個人都有過去<br />\n而且每個人心入面都會define自己最愛嘅一任<br />\n但對方講出黎嗰下原來真係扣血扣得咁勁<br />\n宜家成日諗起都覺得唔開心有條刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問其他巴絲會唔會都覺得呢句嘢hurt到爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定其實係我太耿耿於懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fba741a4ae4804cd632cd1ece7506bc8712c400","tid":319324,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9101ef429a009696974d675fb7d440371ab4c548","tid":319324,"uid":88884,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:56:55.000Z","msg":"叫佢搵返前任囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d53c303c68472c0a808f56381f1d93a7274e04","tid":319324,"uid":116905,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T17:15:31.000Z","msg":"正常都會唔開心<br />\n係咁諗都唔需要同現任講掛"},{"pid":"b379ba7d2612db43c130206d69f7d14e8ac4e64c","tid":319324,"uid":13306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T17:26:57.000Z","msg":"咁你咪做好啲"},{"pid":"3e3434f7fdb25c7f7976161662aeb64fb5532806","tid":319324,"uid":123663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T18:05:06.000Z","msg":"係你條仔on9咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正常咁諗都唔會講出黎啦，係咪想搏你講分手咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6223835f3ed4f04704856f4a9106bf374565d7","tid":319324,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T18:07:57.000Z","msg":"又要問又要介意..."},{"pid":"eac26a6167361e9d46036ab91c97154b51ff94b0","tid":319324,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T18:14:03.000Z","msg":"其實佢係咪on9仔黎<br />\n正常人都唔會係個現任面前咁講<br />\n除非佢係比緊signal你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42b5fe22b3a45f99804e140336f0481776f0dd09","tid":319324,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T18:20:21.000Z","msg":"傻仔"},{"pid":"0cf2e72508cda1e54f764503fab497d7695920b7","tid":319324,"uid":119858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T22:19:13.000Z","msg":"屌 咁你又問<br />\n又要問又想個答案係話你是最好的，有落差又介意<br />\n<br />\n上一個幾好都好依家都分左手同緊你一齊啦<br />\nwho fucking cares? 要數人地拍緊拖果陣sweet既野有排數啦<br />\n<br />\n依家問完又話有條刺 多鬼餘"},{"pid":"19a58ae70ccec527c3916a0357544008814df34c","tid":319324,"uid":96979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T22:30:22.000Z","msg":"現任冇前度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ea2290e91bc739a511c684573dd936bb8b4b23","tid":319324,"uid":96402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:04:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫佢搵返前任囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地冇聯絡幾年啦"},{"pid":"d50145e4561f208b7f3f11e123f622b50a1968a7","tid":319324,"uid":96402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:05:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常都會唔開心<br />\n係咁諗都唔需要同現任講掛</blockquote><br />\nexactly<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  所以我嗰下真係措手不及<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d5c235a2a413496d819296dfd7cc57e27d408e","tid":319324,"uid":96402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:05:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你咪做好啲</blockquote><br />\n已經盡最大能力去做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b566e764373e7239446681385d6ef7563c20a03","tid":319324,"uid":96402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:06:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係你條仔on9咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正常咁諗都唔會講出黎啦，係咪想搏你講分手咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該唔係<br />\n所以佢應該真係on9<br />\n所以佢應該真係好認真咁覺得佢前任係最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27553b5a8ae7924b912a71e12141d2984deb4d3","tid":319324,"uid":18465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:06:41.000Z","msg":"前度係要擺係心裡面"},{"pid":"c6659592c4536b127ae5d66753b05dc659026040","tid":319324,"uid":117752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:06:54.000Z","msg":"得唔到永遠都係最好"},{"pid":"e989106837f86791ed638e28a895fd27947be664","tid":319324,"uid":96402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:08:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又要問又要介意...</blockquote><br />\n咁你點都唔會expect個答案係呢個掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n預咗佢可能話某某前度呢方面比我好 <br />\n但唔會突然話 <br />\n上一任係同任何人都冇得比咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a9d32ad61a95a096a8e1cf223c234524e7dde5","tid":319324,"uid":10621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真係無撚腦 係咁諗都唔好咁講啦"},{"pid":"ae3b99f261612ffaa26f1e92223c26507b1a2346","tid":319324,"uid":96402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:09:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實佢係咪on9仔黎<br />\n正常人都唔會係個現任面前咁講<br />\n除非佢係比緊signal你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢好認真咁講㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以佢係好認真咁覺得佢前度係最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但應該唔會比緊signal我 <br />\n因為我地去緊其他地方玩同stay over"},{"pid":"f4d90412d7724b6b7a14b213d276ce972f5cd548","tid":319324,"uid":96402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:13:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 咁你又問<br />\n又要問又想個答案係話你是最好的，有落差又介意<br />\n<br />\n上一個幾好都好依家都分左手同緊你一齊啦<br />\nwho fucking cares? 要數人地拍緊拖果陣sweet既野有排數啦<br />\n<br />\n依家問完又話有條刺 多鬼餘</blockquote><br />\n問完都估到可能會話某某前度某方面會比我好咁樣<br />\n但冇諗過佢突然話上一個係無人可比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你明唔明嗰下係覺得自己無論做得幾好<br />\n對佢有幾好 都永遠唔會比得上佢上一任<br />\n<br />\n其實你講得好有道理 <br />\n我有勸過自己宜家同緊佢一齊嘅係你自己<br />\n但我份人太注重精神戀愛活得有啲辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1e9588655d302bcd25fcc2eb2f488a01144064","tid":319324,"uid":10141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T06:41:58.000Z","msg":"你條仔都好有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}